    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly way to get on the road? This vehicle is ready for some serious TLC! While it's currently in poor condition and will need mechanical and cosmetic work, it's a fantastic opportunity for a handy buyer to bring a classic back to life. It's priced to move and full of potential for the right person!",
